freedom-repression-or-urban-violence/
"https://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/10/23/angola-update-on-press-freedom-
repression-or-urban-
violence/")：本文英文版發表後隔天，「[保護記者協會](http://cpj.org/2010/10/in-angola-popular-
radio-satirist-injured-in-stabbi.php "http://cpj.org/2010/10/in-angola-
popular-radio-satirist-injured-in-stabbi.php")」指出，同一電台另一位記者Antonio Manuel
“Jojó” da Silva在10月22日遭人刺傷，

